                  <td align="left" style="line-height:22px;"><span style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2c262d; line-height:22px;"> Hello, </span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td height="20"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td align="justify" style="line-height:22px;"><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2c262d; line-height:22px; text-align:justify;">The General Data Protection Regulation act is less than 2 days away from taking effect. We're writing to let you know that we've got you covered. As a cyber-security company, we understand the importance of privacy.</p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td height="20"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td align="justify" style="line-height:22px;"><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2c262d; line-height:22px;text-align:justify">We're sending this message to remind you that we're fully compliant with the GDPR. The personal information you have provided us will be stored and used in accordance with the GDPR.</p></td>
                </tr>
                 <tr>
                  <td height="20"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td align="justify" style="line-height:22px;"><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2c262d; line-height:22px;text-align:justify">You will still enjoy all the privileges and legal rights set out in the End User License Agreement you accepted while installing your Bitdefender product, and you will also benefit from the privacy protection controls that the GDPR mandates for European citizens.</p></td>
                </tr>
                 <tr>
                  <td height="20"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td align="justify" style="line-height:22px;"><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #2c262d; line-height:22px;text-align:justify">Our new privacy policy can be read in full online at <a href="https://connect.bitdefender.com/pub/cc?_ri_=X0Gzc2X%3DYQpglLjHJlYQGizeonLiHjYwpRozggfJLBs4vlzbFjzcksskzgOX0JcPdHppLzdaCzdmj3VXtpKX%3DSRSUYURC&_ei_=EolaGGF4SNMvxFF7KucKuWM_5XCwjRB9up-WmajvqWQy9DLFNpRa9w." target="_blank" style="color: #007bed;"><strong>www.bitdefender.com</strong></a>.</p></td>
